---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-32 md:py-64 bg-[#fcfcfc] border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.3em] text-[#3aa693] font-bold uppercase mb-4">
        04 — About
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
        About Me
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 font-light text-justify">
          A last-year student at the Hanoi University of Mining and Geology, I combine academic rigor 
          with a 2-year track record of developing practical solutions during my studies. Based in Hanoi, I am currently focused on 
          developing high-performance backend systems and specialized synchronization tools.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light text-justify">
          My unique expertise lies at the intersection of traditional backend engineering, BIM 
          Integration, and Game development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <h3 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase mb-8">
          Experience
        </h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-slate-200">
            <div class="absolute w-2 h-2 bg-[#3aa693] rounded-full -left-[4.5px] top-2"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 mb-1">06/2025 — 12/2025</p>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">NHP TECH</h4>
            <p class="text-[#3aa693] text-sm font-medium mb-2">Backend Intern Developer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-slate-200">
            <div class="absolute w-2 h-2 bg-slate-300 rounded-full -left-[4.5px] top-2"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 mb-1">2021 — Present</p>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Hanoi University of Mining and Geology</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm italic">Major: Software Engineer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>